==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈɡɑ.ɡəlz/}}
* {{audio|en-us-goggles.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Etymology===
Probably from [[goggle]] from the appearance it gives the wearer.

===Noun===
{{en-plural noun|sg=goggle}}

# {{plural only}} Protective [[eyewear]] set in a flexible frame to fit snugly against the face.
# {{plural of|goggle}}

